Scripts executed via cron for building the LMT2 aggregate
data tables from raw data.

lmt_update_agg        = Top-level script that should be run by cron every hour or so.
lmt_update_ost_agg    = Updates OST hourly aggregate data.
lmt_update_router_agg = Updates router hourly aggregate data.
lmt_update_mds_agg    = Updates MDS hourly aggregate data.
lmt_update_fs_agg     = Updates filesystem-level agg tables from ost agg tables.
lmt_update_other_agg  = Updates all non-hourly OST/Router/MDS aggregate tables

To update all aggregate data, use lmt_agg.sh script (configure first).

Usage:  lmt_agg.sh [-keep] filesys1 [filesys2 ...]

For convenience, use the lmt_agg.cron script to invoke via cron on an hourly basis.

